{"vocabInfos":[{"lsjDefs":"<b> πετροβόλ-ος</b> <br /> (<i>paroxytone</i>), ον, <b>throwing stones</b>, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 5th-6th c.BC: Xenophon Historicus “Historia Graeca (Hellenica)” 2.4.12. \">Refs 5th c.BC+</a>]<br /><Level2><b>__II</b></Level2> <i>substantive</i> πετροβόλος, ὁ, <b>engine for throwing stones</b>, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 2nd c.BC: Polybius Historicus 5.4.6, LXX.Job.41.19, 2nd c.BC: Athenaeus Mechanicus 34.2, etc.\">LXX+2nd c.BC+</a>]; distinguished from καταπέλτης, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 2nd c.BC: Polybius Historicus 8.7.2 (but καταπέλτας ὀξυβελεῖς τε καὶ πετροβόλους 1st c.BC: Diodorus Siculus Historicus 18.51, compare “IG” 22.468.1): _neuter_ πετροβόλα (i.e. ὄργανα), opposed to δορυβόλα, 1st c.AD: Josephus Historicus “Antiquitates Judaicae” 9.10.3. \">Refs 2nd c.BC+</a>]<br /><Level3><b>__II.2</b></Level3> <b>sling</b>, variant in [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" LXX.1Ki.14.14. \">LXX</a>]<br /><Level2><b>__III</b></Level2> λίθοι πετρόβολοι <b>hurled as from a sling</b>, of hailstones,[<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\"LXX.Eze.13.11, 13. \">LXX</a>]","strongNumber":"G8783","accentedUnicode":"πετροβόλος","shortDef":"a slinger; rock throwing","mediumDef":"a slinger; rock throwing","stepGloss":"a slinger","stepTransliteration":"petrobolos","count":0,"_step_Type":"word"}]}